		<category scheme="https://www.w3.org/blog/news" term="Uncategorized" />
		<summary type="html"><![CDATA[The Second Screen Working Group Patent Advisory Group (PAG), launched in August 2021 in response to disclosures related to a specification of the Second Screen Working Group, has issued a Call for Prior Art to seek prior art that is available in the public domain or on terms consistent with W3C&#8217;s Royalty-Free Licensing Requirements. Public [&#8230;]]]></summary>

					<content type="html" xml:base="https://www.w3.org/blog/news/archives/9355"><![CDATA[<p>The <a href="https://www.w3.org/2021/08/secondscreen-pag/">Second Screen Working Group Patent Advisory Group (PAG)</a>, <a href="https://www.w3.org/blog/news/archives/9201">launched in August 2021</a> in response to <a href="https://www.w3.org/2021/08/secondscreen-pag/#disclosures">disclosures</a> related to a specification of the Second Screen Working Group, has issued a <a href="https://www.w3.org/2021/08/secondscreen-pag/cfpa.html">Call for Prior Art</a> to seek prior art that is available in the public domain or on terms consistent with <a href="https://www.w3.org/Consortium/Patent-Policy-20200915/#sec-Requirements">W3C&#8217;s Royalty-Free Licensing Requirements</a>.</p>
<p>Public comments may be directed to <a href="mailto:public-secondscreen-pag@w3.org">public-secondscreen-pag@w3.org</a> (<a href="https://lists.w3.org/Archives/Public/public-secondscreen-pag/">public archive</a>) by <strong>31 March 2022</strong>. For more information about the Second Screen Working Group PAG, see its <a href="https://www.w3.org/2021/08/secondscreen-pag/">home page</a> and <a href="https://www.w3.org/2021/08/secondscreen-pag/charter.html">charter</a>.</p>
